                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just a quick note to let people know that a cuple of nights ago I helped a few friends the with PoJ exe trial. I had noticed on a few earlier attempts that I no longer had to summon Kamakaze Ani in with me, so out of interest I DCed a prisoner and dragged him down with me.
<br />

<br />
He popped quite happily into the trial, and then, once we had done, followed me out again, which they wouldn't do before. He also was hitting, at one point for 490... which is really don't understand, but I'm no complaining about. I have a screenie somewhere...
<br />

<br />
Anyway, handy for a few more stress free DPS.
<br />

<br />
I'd also be interested to hear about people charming actually in trials. Is this doable? Does it mess up waves?
<br />

<br />
Sol
<br />

<br />
x</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=310187" target="_blank" class="postlink">Soleta Naiia</a>
<br />
Coercer
