                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Charming works fine in trials, I always did it. It's really the only viable way for enchanters to contribute in some trials (like exe).
<br />

<br />
It doesn't mess up the waves if you account for it. In exe you need to kill all 4 mobs to finish a wave, so you break charm after the first 3 are dead then kill pet, repeat each wave.
<br />

<br />
In other trials, like hanging, you can keep your pet the whole trial if you wish. Only 2 of the 4 mobs each wave need to die in that trial...
<br />

<br />
-Belanar</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
