                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">AE'ing the exec trial was the fastest way to go.  I've been in other groups and done the trial without AE, but it's always more fun and seems to be the fastest and most sure win.  When I did this I was level 59 with about 1k unbuffed hp (hee hee.. my how I've grown).
<br />

<br />
Chain stunning in an AE group is the key to winning.  Lead off the wave with AE tash and then just use the 3 main color spells.  Reapply rune at the end of each fight and be sure to use your mod rod early.
<br />

<br />
When not in an AE group, follow normal practices for mezzing.  Dont really worry about slow as your mana and time can be better spent casting nukes.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=398646" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fadnae Vantempla</a>
<br />
